{"tid":1906469,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"簡介下公務員(文職) 有機會拎到既津貼","createTime":"2020-03-02T03:23:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T06:45:13.000Z","uid":34410,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"89219d2b255ab8916b12ee6726fb5e91af90fb47","tid":1906469,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T03:23:52.000Z","msg":"我都係幾種我拎過既津貼，有其他既各巴絲可以補充下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.) 本地膳食津貼<br />\n通常連續返12個鐘先有，平時好難拎到，係黑警先有特權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\npt 6以下 $69<br />\npt 7-13 $103<br />\npt 14-33 $130<br />\npt34 以上 $137<br />\n<br />\n2.) 輪班津貼<br />\n(2000-0700時間當值先計) <br />\n半份(25-50個鐘以下) $663<br />\n全份(50個鐘或以上) $1315<br />\n<br />\n3.) 隨時候召津貼<br />\n姐係可能半夜收call特突返工咁<br />\n半份(96-250個鐘)  $329<br />\n全份(250個鐘以上) $659<br />\n<br />\n4.) 辛勞津貼<br />\n8號波以上或者黑雨都有<br />\n當ot出大鐘(月薪/140)<br />\n<br />\n5.)逾時津貼 ot <br />\n大鐘<br />\n細鐘(月薪/210)<br />\n大細鐘既分別好似係因為文職同紀律部隊既工作時間差左4個鐘一個禮拜"},{"pid":"57225db44e6343e3236554507e4e0d07f9101917","tid":1906469,"uid":171586,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T03:25:56.000Z","msg":"消防有冇"},{"pid":"60b52c9d387d974b8be232c768281c88823c25ad","tid":1906469,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57225db44e6343e3236554507e4e0d07f9101917","tid":1906469,"uid":171586,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T03:25:56.000Z","msg":"消防有冇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T03:36:11.000Z","msg":"冇記錯2,3,4都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 紀律部隊有好多其他津貼既"},{"pid":"35974e43e04c0331a265bb6d713f035ae626fb28","tid":1906469,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T03:46:11.000Z","msg":"文職同紀律部隊既工作時間差左4個鐘一個禮拜<br />\n<br />\n睇你同邊個紀律部隊比啫，入境係39hrs架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"870f74d09c475918a85bacd72775763336544799","tid":1906469,"u